
--create
Creates database from /server/config. Defaults to 'epoch'

--recreate
Use with caution! Deletes and creates database from same parameters as --create

--update
Pushes database update. (Updates ddoc for CouchDB.)

--seed
Seeds database with test data.

-i, --import <importer>
Imports via /importers/<importer>. Edit importers as needed.
